            "text": "449 - "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «لَمَّا مَاتَ إِسْمَاعِيلُ أَمَرْتُ بِهِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "هُوَ مُسَجًّى أَنْ يُكْشَفَ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " عَنْ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "وَجْهِهِ فَقَبَّلْتُ جَبْهَتَهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "ذَقَنَهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "نَحْرَهُ ثُمَّ أَمَرْتُ بِهِ فَغُطِّيَ ثُمَّ قُلْتُ اِكْشِفُوا عَنْهُ فَقَبَّلْتُ أَيْضاً جَبْهَتَهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "ذَقَنَهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "نَحْرَهُ ثُمَّ أَمَرْتُهُمْ فَغَطَّوْهُ ثُمَّ أَمَرْتُ بِهِ فَغُسِّلَ ثُمَّ دَخَلْتُ عَلَيْهِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "قَدْ كُفِّنَ فَقُلْتُ اِكْشِفُوا"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " عَنْ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "وَجْهِهِ فَقَبَّلْتُ جَبْهَتَهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "ذَقَنَهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "نَحْرَهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "عَوَّذْتُهُ ثُمَّ قُلْتُ أَدْرِجُوهُ فَقِيلَ لَهُ بِأَيِّ شَيْءٍ عَوَّذْتَهُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " فَقَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:25:51",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/25/449",
      "text": [
        " بِالْقُرْآنِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.449 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"When (my son) Ismail died, I ordered that his body, while covered, be uncovered so that I could kiss his forehead, chin, and neck.\nThen, I had him covered again and later ordered that he be uncovered a second time, and I kissed his forehead, chin, and neck once more. Then, I had him covered again.\nAfter that, I instructed that he be washed. When the washing was completed, I entered while he was being shrouded and said: 'Uncover his face,' and I kissed his forehead, chin, and neck and then recited protective supplications over him.\nI then said: 'Wrap him.'\nSomeone asked: 'With what did you offer the protective supplication?'\nImam (as) replied: 'With the Qur'an.'\""
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications"
    ]
  },
